{"tid":1464042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(心態)今日就放公安走啦，冇錯","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:02:18.000Z","uid":87100,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"476f0d8e0e7a888a36e0f2f2b49c9eb383aae64c","tid":1464042,"uid":87100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:18:20.000Z","msg":"完？no sorry<br />\n聽日就五花大綁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後日就除衫除褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實任你發揮<br />\n<br />\n點解要咁？<br />\n因為喺機場好多和理非<br />\n我地要做到永遠企喺高地，係佢地先撩者賤，一步一步嚟，和理非先會適應<br />\n<br />\n勇武何嘗未試過做和理非？<br />\n一步一步由時勢逼成<br />\n<br />\n記住沉著，不分化，保持警覺，唔係同路人就越來越少，需要就休息一下，放心交俾佢地<br />\n<br />\n同埋要人多先可以自然令機場取消航班，大家聽日見，多啲人，一齊加油，好冇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ade96132845fc3e60774d2c32fb11f166be632e","tid":1464042,"uid":87100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:20:39.000Z","msg":"push 唔啱請屌<br />\n以我發夢觀察分析<br />\n佢地要心理準備"},{"pid":"ab23f1cb1f2e945f703f8a3b68fe9d1327e34d68","tid":1464042,"uid":87100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:23:14.000Z","msg":"同意幫手推推。唔忍心見到大家自己人嘈，冇意思。警狗依家笑緊大家，因為聽日會更少人。"},{"pid":"8bf955df4c3e0075dc27862036b5eb18d7c7ac6e","tid":1464042,"uid":87100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:25:07.000Z","msg":"同意可唔可以幫手推下，求咁多位手足"},{"pid":"085fb30a6d1a62bbadf3182f078424464f9602a0","tid":1464042,"uid":87100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:25:54.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28671917fae8d676b6bd964330b9048edbb6a784","tid":1464042,"uid":87100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:27:06.000Z","msg":"我再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b86862dec70d25c08bc55ee2a3b010371016f91","tid":1464042,"uid":285660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:29:22.000Z","msg":"無錯, 留佢係度越耐 , 咪比班共狗可以借題發揮"},{"pid":"da21ff55fba852546c3cc4778c1890a29801b256","tid":1464042,"uid":87100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:29:47.000Z","msg":"push呀push<br />\n太多3毛趁大家發夢推緊分化post<br />\n手足們要醒了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33064b267228f3f6d28f1b7fe7de31bffd3252c3","tid":1464042,"uid":87100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b86862dec70d25c08bc55ee2a3b010371016f91","tid":1464042,"uid":285660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:29:22.000Z","msg":"無錯, 留佢係度越耐 , 咪比班共狗可以借題發揮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:31:14.000Z","msg":"係，沉住氣呀大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好搞到和理非聽日唔想出，我地要人呀！人呀！"},{"pid":"a3a5fd6749dd6aaae947f237a1722fc745e4b868","tid":1464042,"uid":6363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:31:31.000Z","msg":"大家聽住。<br />\n知唔知點解政府811咁撚豬會畀你地影到示威者入面有鬼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而唔繼續鬼落去<br />\n<br />\n其實佢地呢招好撚高，政府知我地核彈都唔撚割。所以特登話你知：我地放咗鬼喺你度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等你次次都疑神疑鬼，等戰友間失去咗互相信任。<br />\n<br />\n大家諗吓，由612 走到而家，我地本住一句核彈都唔割先得。所以，所有檢討post，要等該日完咗先好出。仲有唔好懷疑自己身邊嘅人，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">戰友總畀警鬼多</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆、不譴責、不篤灰、不分化、不足鬼<br />\n</span></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3b79ec69dd8508ccd08d3a5c52a421d0d8c788c2","tid":1464042,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:32:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter/閘口出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了，無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},{"pid":"5038f2c0c5eb7709beb38b418b8f77ddc61cdd74","tid":1464042,"uid":87100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3a5fd6749dd6aaae947f237a1722fc745e4b868","tid":1464042,"uid":6363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:31:31.000Z","msg":"大家聽住。<br />\n知唔知點解政府811咁撚豬會畀你地影到示威者入面有鬼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而唔繼續鬼落去<br />\n<br />\n其實佢地呢招好撚高，政府知我地核彈都唔撚割。所以特登話你知：我地放咗鬼喺你度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等你次次都疑神疑鬼，等戰友間失去咗互相信任。<br />\n<br />\n大家諗吓，由612 走到而家，我地本住一句核彈都唔割先得。所以，所有檢討post，要等該日完咗先好出。仲有唔好懷疑自己身邊嘅人，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">戰友總畀警鬼多</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆、不譴責、不篤灰、不分化、不足鬼<br />\n</span></strong></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:35:20.000Z","msg":"都啱！我凌晨出可能好啲 大家會放低情緒分析<br />\n謝指教"},{"pid":"a22acdcd8ea9bfaf89f6e11bea32b5f98be00620","tid":1464042,"uid":87100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b79ec69dd8508ccd08d3a5c52a421d0d8c788c2","tid":1464042,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:32:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter/閘口出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了，無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:37:13.000Z","msg":"要夠人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今日唔夠人，佢地係迫不得已，大家體諒，加油"},{"pid":"c518ec33785e4dab6e78cdfa